wiki.content:
"Alejandro" is the 3rd single from Lady Gaga's 2nd studio album: "The Fame Monster". It was written by Lady Gaga and RedOne. Every song in the album represents a "fear" of some "monster". This song, in the words of Gaga represents "The fear of men monster".
